This quote acknowledges that everyone, has the ability and agency to create their own opportunities. It encourages taking action and being proactive in achieving one's goals and aspirations.

In this post, I will share my story of starting from scratch and how seeking out unique opportunities and taking initiatives led me to an exciting career path.


-- ds.h1: Startups

I was looking up for a job that would offer me more than just a paycheck. I sought for a fresh and exciting career path with the potential for growth and development along with flexible work environment and being a part of innovations.

I believed that Startup is the place to make a meaningful impact and play an important role in building something from the ground up. Startups brings a dynamic and innovative environment, where I can learn new skills, take on new challenges, and grow both personally and professionally. Ultimately, I believe that working for a startup will provide me with the opportunity to make a real difference and help shape the future of a growing company.

